DETERMINING YOUR LICENSE TYPE

If you are unsure whether your use case requires a commercial license, 
please contact us. Generally:

ACADEMIC/NON-COMMERCIAL USE (Free):
- University research projects
- Educational use in academic courses
- Non-profit research organizations
- Personal academic research
- Open source academic projects

COMMERCIAL USE (License Required):
- Biotechnology companies
- Pharmaceutical companies
- Commercial research organizations
